variable_label: PCQ: I A1.  you felt so good or hyper that other people thought you were not your normal self
PCQ: I A2.  you were so irritable that you shouted at people or started fights or arguments
PCQ: I A3.  you felt much more self-confident than usual
PCQ: I A4.  you got much less sleep than usual and found you didnt really miss it
PCQ: I A5.  you were much more talkative or spoke faster than usual
PCQ: I A6.  thoughts raced through your head or you couldnt slow your mind down
PCQ: I A7. you were so easily distracted by things around you that you had trouble concentrating
PCQ: I A8. you had much more energy than usual
PCQ: I A9. you were much more active or did many more things than usual
PCQ: I A10. you were much more social or outgoing than usual for example you telephoned friends in the middle of the night
PCQ: I A11.  you were much more interested in sex than usual
PCQ: I A12. you did things that were unusual for you or that other people might have thought were excessive
PCQ: I A13. spending money got you or your family into trouble
PCQ: IB. Have several of these ever happened during the same period of time
PCQ: IC. How much of a problem did any of these cause you?
